<h2>Tutorial 2. Cutting and Sewing a Mock-up. </h2>
<p></p>
<p>We have already cut and sewn mock-ups before so I assume you have already accustomed yourself to the whole procedure. I believe <strong>illustrating it with comment-free pictures should be more than enough. </strong></p>
<p>
<img src="https://corsetacademy.s3.amazonaws.com/Transparent_corsets/corset_3/Tutorial%202_files/image002.jpg" class="img-responsive center-block"></p>
<p></p>
<p>
<img src="https://corsetacademy.s3.amazonaws.com/Transparent_corsets/corset_3/Tutorial%202_files/image004.jpg" class="img-responsive center-block"></p>
<p>
<img src="https://corsetacademy.s3.amazonaws.com/Transparent_corsets/corset_3/Tutorial%202_files/image006.jpg" class="img-responsive center-block"></p>
<p></p>
<p>
<img src="https://corsetacademy.s3.amazonaws.com/Transparent_corsets/corset_3/Tutorial%202_files/image008.jpg" class="img-responsive center-block"></p>
<p></p>
<p>
<img src="https://corsetacademy.s3.amazonaws.com/Transparent_corsets/corset_3/Tutorial%202_files/image010.jpg" class="img-responsive center-block"></p>
<p></p>
<p>
<img src="https://corsetacademy.s3.amazonaws.com/Transparent_corsets/corset_3/Tutorial%202_files/image012.jpg" class="img-responsive center-block"></p>
<p></p>
<p>
<img src="https://corsetacademy.s3.amazonaws.com/Transparent_corsets/corset_3/Tutorial%202_files/image014.jpg" class="img-responsive center-block"></p>
<p></p>
<p><strong>I start assembling the mock-up. </strong></p>
<p>
<img src="https://corsetacademy.s3.amazonaws.com/Transparent_corsets/corset_3/Tutorial%202_files/image016.jpg" class="img-responsive center-block"></p>
<p><strong>I join the central piece with the intermediate one. </strong></p>
<p>
<img src="https://corsetacademy.s3.amazonaws.com/Transparent_corsets/corset_3/Tutorial%202_files/image018.jpg" class="img-responsive center-block"></p>
<p></p>
<p><strong>I topstitch the seam allowance. </strong></p>
<p></p>
<p><strong><br>
<img src="https://corsetacademy.s3.amazonaws.com/Transparent_corsets/corset_3/Tutorial%202_files/image020.jpg" class="img-responsive center-block"></strong></p>
<p><strong>And do the same thing from the other side of the corset. </strong></p>
<p></p>
<p><strong><br>
<img src="https://corsetacademy.s3.amazonaws.com/Transparent_corsets/corset_3/Tutorial%202_files/image022.jpg" class="img-responsive center-block"></strong></p>
<p></p>
<p><strong><br>
<img src="https://corsetacademy.s3.amazonaws.com/Transparent_corsets/corset_3/Tutorial%202_files/image024.jpg" class="img-responsive center-block"></strong></p>
<p></p>
<p><strong>Then I join the intermediate front piece with the side one. </strong></p>
<p><strong><br>
<img src="https://corsetacademy.s3.amazonaws.com/Transparent_corsets/corset_3/Tutorial%202_files/image026.jpg" class="img-responsive center-block"></strong></p>
<p></p>
<p><strong>I topstitch the seam allowance. </strong></p>
<p><strong><br>
<img src="https://corsetacademy.s3.amazonaws.com/Transparent_corsets/corset_3/Tutorial%202_files/image028.jpg" class="img-responsive center-block"></strong></p>
<p></p>
<p><strong>And I repeat the same procedure from the other side of the corset. </strong></p>
<p><strong><br>
<img src="https://corsetacademy.s3.amazonaws.com/Transparent_corsets/corset_3/Tutorial%202_files/image030.jpg" class="img-responsive center-block"></strong></p>
<p></p>
<p><strong><br>
<img src="https://corsetacademy.s3.amazonaws.com/Transparent_corsets/corset_3/Tutorial%202_files/image032.jpg" class="img-responsive center-block"></strong></p>
<p></p>
<p><strong>Next I join the side front piece with the corset back. </strong></p>
<p><strong><br>
<img src="https://corsetacademy.s3.amazonaws.com/Transparent_corsets/corset_3/Tutorial%202_files/image034.jpg" class="img-responsive center-block"></strong></p>
<p></p>
<p><strong>I topstitch the seam allowance. </strong></p>
<p></p>
<p><strong><br>
<img src="https://corsetacademy.s3.amazonaws.com/Transparent_corsets/corset_3/Tutorial%202_files/image036.jpg" class="img-responsive center-block"></strong></p>
<p></p>
<p><strong>And I sew the other side seam and topstitch its seam allowance. </strong></p>
<p><strong><br>
<img src="https://corsetacademy.s3.amazonaws.com/Transparent_corsets/corset_3/Tutorial%202_files/image038.jpg" class="img-responsive center-block"></strong></p>
<p></p>
<p><strong><br>
<img src="https://corsetacademy.s3.amazonaws.com/Transparent_corsets/corset_3/Tutorial%202_files/image040.jpg" class="img-responsive center-block"></strong></p>
<p></p>
<p><strong>Then I join the side back piece with the central back piece. </strong></p>
<p><strong><br>
<img src="https://corsetacademy.s3.amazonaws.com/Transparent_corsets/corset_3/Tutorial%202_files/image042.jpg" class="img-responsive center-block"></strong></p>
<p></p>
<p><strong>And I topstitch the seam allowance. </strong></p>
<p></p>
<p><strong><br>
<img src="https://corsetacademy.s3.amazonaws.com/Transparent_corsets/corset_3/Tutorial%202_files/image044.jpg" class="img-responsive center-block"></strong></p>
<p></p>
<p><strong>I do the same from the other side of the back. </strong></p>
<p><strong><br>
<img src="https://corsetacademy.s3.amazonaws.com/Transparent_corsets/corset_3/Tutorial%202_files/image046.jpg" class="img-responsive center-block"></strong></p>
<p></p>
<p><strong><br>
<img src="https://corsetacademy.s3.amazonaws.com/Transparent_corsets/corset_3/Tutorial%202_files/image048.jpg" class="img-responsive center-block"></strong></p>
<p></p>
<p><strong>And I start assembling the cups. </strong></p>
<p><strong><br>
<img src="https://corsetacademy.s3.amazonaws.com/Transparent_corsets/corset_3/Tutorial%202_files/image050.jpg" class="img-responsive center-block"></strong></p>
<p><strong><br>
<img src="https://corsetacademy.s3.amazonaws.com/Transparent_corsets/corset_3/Tutorial%202_files/image052.jpg" class="img-responsive center-block"></strong></p>
<p><strong><br>
<img src="https://corsetacademy.s3.amazonaws.com/Transparent_corsets/corset_3/Tutorial%202_files/image054.jpg" class="img-responsive center-block"></strong></p>
<p></p>
<p><strong><br>
<img src="https://corsetacademy.s3.amazonaws.com/Transparent_corsets/corset_3/Tutorial%202_files/image056.jpg" class="img-responsive center-block"></strong></p>
<p><strong><br>
<img src="https://corsetacademy.s3.amazonaws.com/Transparent_corsets/corset_3/Tutorial%202_files/image058.jpg" class="img-responsive center-block"></strong></p>
<p></p>
<p><strong><br>
<img src="https://corsetacademy.s3.amazonaws.com/Transparent_corsets/corset_3/Tutorial%202_files/image060.jpg" class="img-responsive center-block"></strong></p>
<p></p>
<p><strong><br>
<img src="https://corsetacademy.s3.amazonaws.com/Transparent_corsets/corset_3/Tutorial%202_files/image062.jpg" class="img-responsive center-block"></strong></p>
<p></p>
<p><strong><br>
<img src="https://corsetacademy.s3.amazonaws.com/Transparent_corsets/corset_3/Tutorial%202_files/image064.jpg" class="img-responsive center-block"></strong></p>
<p></p>
<p><strong>I make a stay-stitch along the rounded edge of the cup. </strong></p>
<p><strong><br>
<img src="https://corsetacademy.s3.amazonaws.com/Transparent_corsets/corset_3/Tutorial%202_files/image066.jpg" class="img-responsive center-block"></strong></p>
<p><strong>I fold the seam allowance inwards over the stay-stitch and secure it. </strong></p>
<p><strong><br>
<img src="https://corsetacademy.s3.amazonaws.com/Transparent_corsets/corset_3/Tutorial%202_files/image068.jpg" class="img-responsive center-block"></strong></p>
<p><strong><br>
<img src="https://corsetacademy.s3.amazonaws.com/Transparent_corsets/corset_3/Tutorial%202_files/image070.jpg" class="img-responsive center-block"></strong></p>
<p><strong>And I perform the same procedure with the second cup. </strong></p>
<p><strong>I pin the cup to the body. </strong></p>
<p><strong><br>
<img src="https://corsetacademy.s3.amazonaws.com/Transparent_corsets/corset_3/Tutorial%202_files/image072.jpg" class="img-responsive center-block"></strong></p>
<p><strong>And sew it in. </strong></p>
<p><strong><br>
<img src="https://corsetacademy.s3.amazonaws.com/Transparent_corsets/corset_3/Tutorial%202_files/image073.jpg" class="img-responsive center-block"></strong></p>
<p><strong>And I do the same with the second cup. </strong></p>
<p><strong><br>
<img src="https://corsetacademy.s3.amazonaws.com/Transparent_corsets/corset_3/Tutorial%202_files/image074.jpg" class="img-responsive center-block"></strong></p>
<p></p>
<p><strong><br>
<img src="https://corsetacademy.s3.amazonaws.com/Transparent_corsets/corset_3/Tutorial%202_files/image075.jpg" class="img-responsive center-block"></strong></p>
